      *
           IF      ORCHC14-KBN         =   "1"
               MOVE    "予約一覧表"        TO  HC14-TITLE
           ELSE
               MOVE    "未院一覧表"        TO  HC14-TITLE
           END-IF
      *    診療日
           MOVE    WRK-HENYMDG         TO  HC14-SRYYMD
      *
           PERFORM 400-PRINT-SEC
      *
           INITIALIZE                  HC14
           MOVE    ZERO                TO  IDX
           .
       200-HC14-PRINT-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *****************************************************************
      *    帳票編集処理
      *****************************************************************
       300-HC14-HEN-SEC                SECTION.
      *
      *    連番号
           ADD     1                   TO  WRK-LINE
           MOVE    WRK-LINE            TO  WRK-ZZ9
           MOVE    WRK-ZZ9             TO  HC14-NUM   (IDX)
      *    患者番号
           IF      YYK-PTID            =   ZERO
               MOVE    SPACE               TO  HC14-PTNUM  (IDX)
           ELSE
               PERFORM 3001-KNJNO-HENSYU-SEC
               MOVE    WRK-PTNUM           TO  HC14-PTNUM  (IDX)
           END-IF
      *    患者名称
           MOVE    YYK-NAME            TO  HC14-NAME   (IDX)
      *    予約時間
           MOVE    YYK-YYKTIME(1:2)    TO  HC14-YYKTIME (IDX)(1:2)
           MOVE    ":"                 TO  HC14-YYKTIME (IDX)(3:1)
           MOVE    YYK-YYKTIME(3:2)    TO  HC14-YYKTIME (IDX)(4:2)
      *    ドクター
           PERFORM VARYING     IDX-D   FROM    1   BY  1
                   UNTIL      (IDX-D   >   99  )
                          OR  (TBL-DRCD (IDX-D)    =   SPACE)
               IF     YYK-DRCD             =   TBL-DRCD (IDX-D)
                   MOVE    TBL-DRCDNAME (IDX-D)
                                           TO  HC14-DRNAME (IDX)
                   MOVE    99              TO  IDX-D
               END-IF
           END-PERFORM
      *    診療内容をセット
           PERFORM VARYING     IDX-D   FROM    1   BY  1
                   UNTIL      (IDX-D   >   99  )
                          OR  (TBL-SRYNAIYO (IDX-D)    =   SPACE)
               IF     YYK-SRYNAIYO         =   TBL-SRYNAIYO (IDX-D)
                   MOVE    TBL-SRYNAIYOMEI (IDX-D)
                                           TO  HC14-SRYNAIYO (IDX)
                   MOVE    99              TO  IDX-D
               END-IF
           END-PERFORM
      *
      *    来院済み
           IF      YYK-RAIINZUMI       =   "1"
               MOVE    "済"            TO  HC14-RAIIN  (IDX)
           END-IF
      *
      *    診療科
           PERFORM VARYING     IDX-D   FROM    1   BY  1
                   UNTIL      (IDX-D   >   99  )
                          OR  (TBL-SRYKA-CD (IDX-D)    =   SPACE)
               IF     YYK-SRYKA            =   TBL-SRYKA-CD (IDX-D)
                   MOVE    TBL-SRYKANAME (IDX-D)
                                           TO  HC14-SRYKA  (IDX)
                   MOVE    99              TO  IDX-D
               END-IF
           END-PERFORM
      *
      *    予約確認連絡コード
           PERFORM VARYING     IDX-D   FROM    1   BY  1
                   UNTIL      (IDX-D   >   9   )
                          OR  (TBL-RENRAK-CD (IDX-D)   =   SPACE)
               IF     YYK-KAKREN            =   TBL-RENRAK-CD (IDX-D)
                   MOVE    TBL-YYKKAKNAME (IDX-D)
                                           TO  HC14-RENRAKU  (IDX)
                   MOVE    9               TO  IDX-D
               END-IF
           END-PERFORM
      *
      *    予約内容コード
           PERFORM VARYING     IDX-D   FROM    1   BY  1
                   UNTIL      (IDX-D   >   99   )
                          OR  (TBL-YYKKBN-CD (IDX-D)   =   SPACE)
               IF     YYK-YYKKBN            =   TBL-YYKKBN-CD (IDX-D)
                   MOVE    TBL-YYKKBNNAME (IDX-D)
                                           TO  HC14-YOYAKUNAIY (IDX)
                   MOVE    99              TO  IDX-D
               END-IF
           END-PERFORM
      *
           .
       310-HC14-HEN-EXT.
           EXIT.
